{
  "texts": [
    "The SocraTest framework outlines a comprehensive vision for such an autonomous, conversational test agent [41].",
    "These advancements demonstrate the feasibility of autonomous agents in LLM-based test generation.",
    "Automated Prompt Engineering.Although prompt engineering has proven effective, its success remains heavily dependent on the experience and intuition of human experts, rendering it more of a \"craft\" than a \"systematic science\".",
    "To overcome this dependency, recent research has begun to explore automated prompt optimization (APO), a paradigm that leverages AI to automatically discover optimal instructions for AI models.For instance, the MAPS [47] framework automatically optimizes test generation prompts for specific LLMs based on test effectiveness, such as code coverage.",
    "It achieves this through two core mechanisms."
  ]
}